page.title: 08MY TYPICAL DAY (DEAN 10YRS)
page.content:
{A TYPICAL DAY IN THE LIFE OF DEAN {MONARCH PUPL AT MURTON JUBILEE COUNTY {JUNIOR MIXED AND INFANT SCHOOL.
One day I was in bed when I heard my mam it was twenty past eight on a Thursday morning. I was still half asleep so I got out of bed and went down the stairs. We slept in so I rushed my breakfast down,got ready,washed my hands and face and cleaned my teeth.Now it was quarter to nine.I ran to school as fast as I could I was just in the yard when the whistle went.Normal day at school; got wrong.Then it was half past three home time.I walked home got changed went out to play came in at eight 0'clock watch T.V.go to bed half past nine.
